Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.90,0:02:41.22,English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1000)}Já hledala v místech,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.50,0:02:47.29,Romanji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1000)}sagašitekitakedo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.50,0:02:47.29,English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1000)}kde vítr vanul,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.29,0:02:52.02,Romanji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}hitori sora wo miagete
