Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.02,0:02:55.56,English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,600)}Pak trochu si zdřímla,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.32,0:03:05.79,Romanji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1000)}wasureteitta kučinaši no nioi kandžite
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.32,0:03:05.79,English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1000)}s nosem plným gardénií.
